46
00:02:34,810 --> 00:02:38,120
Ms. Koh! Aaprubahan ko ba ito, o hindi?

47
00:02:38,320 --> 00:02:41,090
Pagkatapos ay sasakupin ko rin ang shift.

48
00:02:44,120 --> 00:02:48,090
Sa pag-cover naming tatlo,
dapat marunong kaming mag-manage.

49
00:02:49,190 --> 00:02:50,400
Batang Hee.

50
