132
00:07:28,110 --> 00:07:29,786
Stomp.

133
00:07:29,810 --> 00:07:33,350
- Maglinis ka.
- Maglinis ka.

134
00:07:33,450 --> 00:07:35,786
- Jong Hee. Magaling ako dito diba?
- Oo? Ikaw ang pinakamahusay.

135
00:07:35,810 --> 00:07:37,126
- Ako rin, tama?
- Ang pinakamahusay!

136
00:07:37,150 --> 00:07:38,850
- Mas mahirap! Stomp.
- Jong Hee.

137
00:07:39,450 --> 00:07:41,126
- Yeong Rye!
- Yeong Rye!

138
00:07:41,150 --> 00:07:42,150
nandito ka?

139
00:07:43,020 --> 00:07:45,290
Anong ginagawa mo dito ng hindi sinasabi sa akin?

140
00:07:46,420 --> 00:07:47,630
