- Talaga?
- Oo.

992
01:07:58,300 --> 01:07:59,600
Gagawin mo talaga yun?

993
01:08:00,300 --> 01:08:01,300
Oo.

994
01:08:07,610 --> 01:08:08,610
Okay.

995
01:08:10,280 --> 01:08:11,280
Sige, kung ganoon.

996
01:08:13,380 --> 01:08:15,120
Pupunta ako para tumawag.

997
01:08:15,320 --> 01:08:17,296
Tapusin mo ito, at mag-ayos ka lang ng kaunti.

998
01:08:17,320 --> 01:08:18,320
Okay.

999
01:08:51,450 --> 01:08:53,320
Oo, hello?

1000
01:08:58,860 --> 01:09:00,030
Hello?

1001
01:09:06,430 --> 01:09:07,500
Hello?

1002
01:09:08,000 --> 01:09:09,940
Kung tatawag ka,
sabihin mo man lang.

1003
01:09:10,470 --> 01:09:11,570
Sino ito?

1004
01:09:12,310 --> 01:09:13,516
Sino ka, punk ka?

1005
01:09:13,540 --> 01:09:16,180
Ang munting brat na ito. Sino
ka, gumagawa ng prank call?

1006
01:09:16,380 --> 01:09:17,680
Sino ka, punk ka?

1007
01:09:20,080 --> 01:09:21,120
Hindi kapani-paniwala.

1008
01:09:23,450 --> 01:09:26,366
Anyway, ang mga taong tulad nito ay dapat
bilugan at ikulong.

1009
01:09:26,390 --> 01:09:27,420
Ang maliliit na punk na ito.

1010
01:09:28,520 --> 01:09:30,320
Masyadong maluwag ang mga batas sa bansang ito .

1011
01:09:48,080 --> 01:09:49,180
Hello?

1012
01:09:49,380 --> 01:09:50,380
Hey.

1013
01:09:51,510 --> 01:09:52,880
Ako ito, Seo Jong Hee.

1014
01:09:54,250 --> 01:09:55,250
Hey.

1015
01:09:56,020 --> 01:09:57,020
ano?

1016
01:09:57,320 --> 01:09:59,920
Nasa isang payphone ako, at
wala na ako sa aking huling sentimos.

1017
01:10:00,220 --> 01:10:01,990
Gagawin ko ito nang mabilis, kaya makinig ka.

1018
01:10:03,320 --> 01:10:04,330
Okay.

1019
01:10:04,430 --> 01:10:06,290
Kilalanin ako sa harap ng
Vivaldi sa Linggo ng 1pm.

1020
01:10:06,890 --> 01:10:09,010
May kailangan
muna akong sabihin sayo ng personal.

1021
