okay ka lang ba? Hindi ka naman nasaktan diba?

1090
01:14:56,550 --> 01:14:58,490
Ay naku. I'm so sorry.

1091
01:14:59,490 --> 01:15:01,460
Biglang na-flat ang gulong.

1092
01:15:01,990 --> 01:15:04,830
Natatakot ako na kailangan mong
bumaba at sumakay sa susunod na bus.

1093
01:15:05,030 --> 01:15:06,860
- Sus.
- I'm sorry.

1094
01:15:08,000 --> 01:15:10,060
- Mangyaring bumaba.
- I'm sorry.

1095
01:15:10,160 --> 01:15:11,776
Lahat, mangyaring lumabas. pasensya na po.

1096
